Barroit
=======

Barroit is a collection of useful scripts and tools designed to simplify system
setup and automation. It includes utilities for tasks such as kernel module
signing automation and rendering PDFs with inverted colors.

Additionally, Barroit provides a quick way to set up a new environment across
different operating systems. It includes VS Code configuration, SSH key setup,
keycode mappings, GDB supplement functions, and more, ensuring a consistent
workflow. Supported platforms include FreeBSD 14, Windows 11, Sequoia, and
Noble.
